y in the major metabolic pathways of toremifene in human liver microsomes." Biochem Pharmacol 47 (1994):  1883-95[4] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[5] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0', 1767365211);
